(16, 1, '2014-10-24 22:09:29', '2014-10-24 22:09:29', 'Liven up your next party or special event by giving them something they''ll truly remember. With his own mix of magic and comedy, Phil Pivnick is the magician who can wow audiences big and small.\r\n\r\nWhether you''re searching for close-up magic or a large scale performance, you’ve found your magician right here. "...with a client list ranging from Greater Toronto Area families, to large corporations and countless non profits, The Magic Guy is amongst the area’s most in demand and busiest magicians for birthday parties, weddings, corporate functions and other special events...."', 'DISCOVER ONE OF THE BEST TORONTO MAGICIANS', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'home', '', '', '2014-11-03 00:18:52', '2014-11-03 00:18:52', '', 0, 'http://localhost/magictoronto/?page_id=16', 0, 'page', '', 0),
