(67, 1, '2014-11-01 02:21:52', '2014-11-01 02:21:52', 'Phil Pivnick is more than a magician. He''s an entertainer. Along with wonder and amazement, his magic acts are packed with plenty of laughs. That means no matter what kind of event you''re planning, whether it''s a birthday party, a wedding or a corporate banquet, you can be sure that your guests will have a great time watching Phil''s magic show. Book a show or get more information now.', 'Are you looking for a Toronto magician?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'are-you-looking-for-a-toronto-magician', '', '', '2014-11-02 06:14:47', '2014-11-02 06:14:47', '', 0, 'http://localhost/magictoronto/?post_type=key-points&#038;p=67', 0, 'key-points', '', 0),
(68, 1, '2014-11-01 02:22:13', '2014-11-01 02:22:13', 'There is more than one style of magic, and you can be sure that there is one that will suit your function perfectly. For events being planned in the home, such as a birthday party, you''ll want to entertain a whole group at once. When it''s a banquet or similar event you''re throwing, having a magician performing close-up magic while your guests mingle or while they''re at their tables may be just the thing!', 'Performing close-up magic, table magic, or magic for large groups, Phil is the magician for you.', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'performing-close-up-magic-table-magic-or-magic-for-large-groups-phil-is-the-magician-for-you', '', '', '2014-11-02 06:14:49', '2014-11-02 06:14:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost/magictoronto/?post_type=key-points&#038;p=68', 0, 'key-points', '', 0),
(69, 1, '2014-11-01 02:22:29', '2014-11-01 02:22:29', 'There are a lot of things to think about when putting a great event together. The last thing you''ll need is to have to change things to suit the whim of the entertainer you hire. Phil has been performing magic long enough to know this, and you can be sure he''ll be able to deliver an act that fits the needs of your event.', 'Entertainment that suits your needs.', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'entertainment-that-suits-your-needs', '', '', '2014-11-02 06:14:48', '2014-11-02 06:14:48', '', 0, 'http://localhost/magictoronto/?post_type=key-points&#038;p=69', 0, 'key-points', '', 0),
(70, 1, '2014-11-01 02:22:48', '2014-11-01 02:22:48', 'When planning parties or other events, the goal is always to show your guests a good time. More than enjoying every moment though, they should also remember those moments for years to come. how do you ensure they''ll be talking about the great time they had long after the day is done? By adding a touch of magic! Those magical moments of astonishment are what stay with people forever, and Phil is just the guy to create those moments for you.', 'Ensure your guests always remember.', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'ensure-your-guests-always-remember', '', '', '2014-11-02 06:14:48', '2014-11-02 06:14:48', '', 0, 'http://localhost/magictoronto/?post_type=key-points&#038;p=70', 0, 'key-points', '', 0),
(71, 1, '2014-11-01 02:23:03', '2014-11-01 02:23:03', 'There isn''t just one magical style, but chances are Phil''s style of performing can fit your needs. Experienced in table hopping, strolling magic and other forms of close-up, he knows how to astound people while performing feats right under their noses. As a performer at birthday parties and on stage at corporate events, he always delivers a killer show.', 'There is more than one style of magic.', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'there-is-more-than-one-style-of-magic', '', '', '2014-11-02 06:14:49', '2014-11-02 06:14:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost/magictoronto/?post_type=key-points&#038;p=71', 0, 'key-points', '', 0),
