(93, 1, '2014-11-01 04:06:17', '2014-11-01 04:06:17', '<div class="two_third_first">\r\n<h2>Toronto Magician for Kids’ Parties</h2>\r\n<div class="leftvideo">http://www.youtube.com/embed/rlO5Lb3N6bw?rel=0&amp;fs=1</div>\r\nThe Magic Guy has over twenty years of professional performing experience, and performs hundreds of shows each year. He''s developed a high energy style, and a show that''s always tailored to each kids'' party.\r\n<h5>Kids will laugh and cheer</h5>\r\nIt''s easy to see why he''s the Greater Toronto Area''s best choice for kids entertainment. Like all great kids'' magicians, Phil will have them roaring with laughter.\r\n<h5>Make your child feel extra special!</h5>\r\nThe Magic Guy keeps the kids involved throughout the show. They will all participate throughout the fast paced act, and some kids will be volunteers in the show, waving wands, playing with exciting props, and helping to make the magic happen. For <a href="toronto_kids_party_magicians.html">birthdays parties</a>, the birthday child will be the star in the show''s best moments!\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Kid Shows (Fun for birthdays & more)', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '92-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-11-01 04:06:17', '2014-11-01 04:06:17', '', 92, 'http://localhost/magictoronto/92-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
