(116, 1, '2014-11-02 12:15:43', '2014-11-02 12:15:43', '<strong>Jumbo Inflatable Wands</strong><br/>2 foot long inflatable magic Jumbo Inflatable Wands! These are quickly becoming a huge hit amongst kids<br/><br/><strong>Magic Loot Bags</strong><br/>Are you planning on giving out loot bags at the birthday party but would like to save the trouble shopping for goodies, and the expense of the leftovers you''re inevitably stuck with? These magic loot bags are a great deal and come with magic props, instructions and an activity booklet.<br/><br/><h3>Don''t get stuck paying for extras. But only those needed the day of the party!</h3>', 'Party Favours & Loot Bags', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'magic-loot-bags', '', '', '2014-11-03 01:18:57', '2014-11-03 01:18:57', '', 0, 'http://localhost/magictoronto/?post_type=products&#038;p=116', 0, 'products', '', 0),
