(118, 1, '2014-11-02 17:16:55', '2014-11-02 17:16:55', 'The birthday party magic shows are always tailored to each audience, so you can be confident the kids will have a wonderful time, whatever their age group. Cheers & Laughter Each fun-filled show opens with high energy routines that get the kids laughing and cheering from the start. Once the show gets going, the laughs just keep coming. You’ll see right away that this is much more than magic.', 'What happens in a 45 minutes Magic Show', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'what-happens-in-a-45-minutes-magic-show', '', '', '2014-11-03 01:23:38', '2014-11-03 01:23:38', '', 0, 'http://localhost/magictoronto/?post_type=key-points&#038;p=118', 0, 'key-points', '', 0),
