(160, 1, '2014-11-03 00:32:28', '2014-11-03 00:32:28', 'Some magicians just do tricks, but The Magic Guy entertains the crowd while doing the impossible. This show is a great addition to entertain a large crowd at events ranging from birthdays and bridal showers to office parties and summer BBQs!', 'Are You Ready to Believe In The Impossible?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'are-you-ready-to-believe-in-the-impossible', '', '', '2014-11-03 01:22:04', '2014-11-03 01:22:04', '', 0, 'http://localhost/magictoronto/?post_type=key-points&#038;p=160', 0, 'key-points', '', 0),
(161, 1, '2014-11-03 00:34:07', '2014-11-03 00:34:07', 'Watching magicians from your seat is fun, but actually getting to be a part of the show is an unforgettable experience. Phil, The Magic Guy, creates an interactive environment without making anyone feel put on the spot.', 'Join In The Magic Show', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'join-in-the-magic-show', '', '', '2014-11-03 01:22:55', '2014-11-03 01:22:55', '', 0, 'http://localhost/magictoronto/?post_type=key-points&#038;p=161', 0, 'key-points', '', 0),
(162, 1, '2014-11-03 00:35:08', '2014-11-03 00:35:08', 'While the magic and presentation is aimed at an adult audience, the shows can be enjoyed by an all ages crowd. The program includes coin and card manipulation, illusions and amazing mentalism.', 'Amazing & Memorable', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'amazing-memorable', '', '', '2014-11-03 01:21:57', '2014-11-03 01:21:57', '', 0, 'http://localhost/magictoronto/?post_type=key-points&#038;p=162', 0, 'key-points', '', 0),
(163, 1, '2014-11-03 00:34:59', '2014-11-03 00:34:59', '', 'magic_guy_rings', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', 'magic_guy_rings', '', '', '2014-11-03 00:34:59', '2014-11-03 00:34:59', '', 162, 'http://localhost/magictoronto/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/magic_guy_rings.png', 0, 'attachment', 'image/png', 0),
(164, 1, '2014-11-03 00:37:09', '2014-11-03 00:37:09', 'Why is this the most powerful style of magic show you''ll ever see? Because the incredible feats happen right under your nose. Strolling magic, also known as table hopping and mingling magic, is the perfect addition to your party.', 'Strolling Magicians Present Magic At Its Best', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'strolling-magicians-present-magic-at-its-best', '', '', '2014-11-03 01:23:25', '2014-11-03 01:23:25', '', 0, 'http://localhost/magictoronto/?post_type=key-points&#038;p=164', 0, 'key-points', '', 0),
(165, 1, '2014-11-03 00:37:54', '2014-11-03 00:37:54', 'Strolling magic is great for any time during an event, but it''s a popular choice to help start things off right. During cocktails at a wedding or the opening of a corporate event, The Magic Guy''s performances help set the mood, and encourage interaction amongst your guests.', 'Break the ice with a touch of mystery', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'break-the-ice-with-a-touch-of-mystery', '', '', '2014-11-03 01:22:21', '2014-11-03 01:22:21', '', 0, 'http://localhost/magictoronto/?post_type=key-points&#038;p=165', 0, 'key-points', '', 0),
(166, 1, '2014-11-03 00:38:35', '2014-11-03 00:38:35', 'Can it really be a trick if you were holding it the whole time? When magicians entertain with their craft this close up, and allow your guests to hold the objects as they transform, multiply or disappear, it creates an amazing and lasting impression.', 'It happens right in your own hands', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'it-happens-right-in-your-own-hands', '', '', '2014-11-03 01:22:10', '2014-11-03 01:22:10', '', 0, 'http://localhost/magictoronto/?post_type=key-points&#038;p=166', 0, 'key-points', '', 0),
(167, 1, '2014-11-03 00:39:58', '2014-11-03 00:39:58', 'The perfect entertainment for smaller gatherings, such as parties held in your home. These 30 to 45 minute magic shows feature an eclectic mix of magical styles that will keep you and your guests amazed and smiling all the way through.', 'Close Up & Intimate Magic Show', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'close-up-intimate-magic-show', '', '', '2014-11-03 01:22:26', '2014-11-03 01:22:26', '', 0, 'http://localhost/magictoronto/?post_type=key-points&#038;p=167', 0, 'key-points', '', 0),
(168, 1, '2014-11-03 00:40:31', '2014-11-03 00:40:31', 'Can it really be a trick if you were holding it the whole time? When magicians entertain with their craft this close up, and allow your guests to hold the objects as they transform, multiply or disappear, it creates an amazing and lasting impression.', 'It happens right in your own hands', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'it-happens-right-in-your-own-hands-2', '', '', '2014-11-03 01:22:39', '2014-11-03 01:22:39', '', 0, 'http://localhost/magictoronto/?post_type=key-points&#038;p=168', 0, 'key-points', '', 0),
(169, 1, '2014-11-03 00:41:10', '2014-11-03 00:41:10', 'Great magicians can perform near-miracles with cards. Toronto''s Magic Guy is no different, but his shows consist of so much more. He''ll introduce many kinds of props throughout his performances, including some of the world''s best illusions with coins.', 'Want more than a bunch of card tricks?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'want-more-than-a-bunch-of-card-tricks', '', '', '2014-11-03 01:23:32', '2014-11-03 01:23:32', '', 0, 'http://localhost/magictoronto/?post_type=key-points&#038;p=169', 0, 'key-points', '', 0),
