(178, 1, '2014-11-03 00:55:11', '2014-11-03 00:55:11', ' ', '', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '178', '', '', '2014-11-03 01:40:33', '2014-11-03 01:40:33', '', 0, 'http://localhost/magictoronto/?p=178', 3, 'nav_menu_item', '', 0),
(179, 1, '2014-11-03 00:59:04', '2014-11-03 00:59:04', 'Phil is a great magician who has performed countless school magic shows across the Toronto area. He brings a show that''s perfect for the venue. It''s an amazing act that''s packed with fun props that the largest of groups can enjoy.', 'Magic For Audiences Big and Small', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'magic-for-audiences-big-and-small', '', '', '2014-11-03 01:23:07', '2014-11-03 01:23:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost/magictoronto/?post_type=key-points&#038;p=179', 0, 'key-points', '', 0),
(180, 1, '2014-11-03 00:59:50', '2014-11-03 00:59:50', 'The program can be tailored to fit the group. If you have a small daycare with a couple dozen toddlers or a big school that will fill the gym with kids of all ages, you can be confident that this school magic show will be exactly what you''re looking for. The comedy perfectly targets old and young alike. The amazing magic will delight the young children and baffle the older ones.', 'Perfect for any grade', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'perfect-for-any-grade', '', '', '2014-11-03 01:23:13', '2014-11-03 01:23:13', '', 0, 'http://localhost/magictoronto/?post_type=key-points&#038;p=180', 0, 'key-points', '', 0),
(181, 1, '2014-11-03 01:00:50', '2014-11-03 01:00:50', 'The Magic Guy''s performs shows that got incredible reviews from staff and kids alike at daycares. These acts are regularly done for groups of a dozen or two up to groups of a hundred. Whether it''s for a special event, a summer-camp or a holiday party, you should contact him today for details on the amazing show he can bring to your daycare.', 'Looking for daycare magicians?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'looking-for-daycare-magicians', '', '', '2014-11-03 01:23:00', '2014-11-03 01:23:00', '', 0, 'http://localhost/magictoronto/?post_type=key-points&#038;p=181', 0, 'key-points', '', 0),
(182, 1, '2014-11-03 01:02:03', '2014-11-03 01:02:03', 'Many of The Toronto Magic Guy''s school shows are put on for individual classes. These smaller shows can take place right in your classroom. In most instances, he brings a bigger show that can be performed on stage for several classes or the whole school. Throughout all of his shows, the children help out from start to finish and love making the magic happen.', 'Elementary and high school magician', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'elementary-and-high-school-magician', '', '', '2014-11-03 01:22:31', '2014-11-03 01:22:31', '', 0, 'http://localhost/magictoronto/?post_type=key-points&#038;p=182', 0, 'key-points', '', 0),
(183, 1, '2014-11-03 01:07:26', '2014-11-03 01:07:26', 'Celebrate the magic of the season with some real live magic! Every year, The Magic Guy puts together a holiday show that’s perfect for Toronto and Area office parties or private functions. Always tailored to suit the audience, you can be sure your guests will have a fun and memorable time whether the audience is children, adults, or a mix of all ages.', 'Something different for the holidays. Something amazing for everyone.', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'something-different-for-the-holidays-something-amazing-for-everyone', '', '', '2014-11-03 01:23:19', '2014-11-03 01:23:19', '', 0, 'http://localhost/magictoronto/?post_type=key-points&#038;p=183', 0, 'key-points', '', 0),
(184, 1, '2014-11-03 01:09:44', '2014-11-03 01:09:44', 'Perfect for holiday parties, the show is filled with laughs, audience interaction and amazing magic that will leave your guests wanting more. If you’re looking for great entertainment for the upcoming Christmas or holiday party, you’ve found it right here. Contact Phil Pivnick, Toronto’s own Magic Guy, today to secure a booking.', '45 minutes of laughter and amazement!', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '45-minutes-of-laughter-and-amazement', '', '', '2014-11-03 01:21:48', '2014-11-03 01:21:48', '', 0, 'http://localhost/magictoronto/?post_type=key-points&#038;p=184', 0, 'key-points', '', 0),
(186, 1, '2014-11-03 01:26:04', '2014-11-03 01:26:04', 'Children are loving these 2 foot long inflatable magic wands. Easy to inflate, self sealing, strong and durable, these wands are a ton of fun, and an awesome alternative to balloon animals. The children will see how cool they are while the Magic Guy actually uses one during the Super & Deluxe magic shows.', 'Jumbo Inflatable Wands', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'jumbo-inflatable-wands-3', '', '', '2014-11-03 01:36:37', '2014-11-03 01:36:37', '', 0, 'http://localhost/magictoronto/?post_type=key-points&#038;p=186', 0, 'key-points', '', 0),
(187, 1, '2014-11-03 01:27:30', '2014-11-03 01:27:30', 'The Magic Guy is now providing magic loot bags for children''s birthday parties, or other events. These goodie bags are packed with magic tricks that are great for kids 5 years and older. Printed instructions are included, along with a web link to <a href="http://www.magicsecrets.ca/">video tutorials</a> so all the children can master their tricks!', 'Magic Loot Bags', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'magic-loot-bags-2', '', '', '2014-11-03 01:36:37', '2014-11-03 01:36:37', '', 0, 'http://localhost/magictoronto/?post_type=key-points&#038;p=187', 0, 'key-points', '', 0),
(188, 1, '2014-11-03 01:29:00', '2014-11-03 01:29:00', 'What makes up this fun loot? Each contains several magic props including a magic wand, a Magic Twisty Worm, and more! There are also printed instructions (and a link to online video lessons!), an awesome activity booklet, and a Magic Guy souvenir magnet.\r\n\r\n*Exact contents may vary without posted notice, but full details will always be available by email or telephone at any times.', 'Inside the birthday party loot bags*', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'inside-the-birthday-party-loot-bags', '', '', '2014-11-03 01:36:36', '2014-11-03 01:36:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/magictoronto/?post_type=key-points&#038;p=188', 0, 'key-points', '', 0),
(189, 1, '2014-11-03 01:30:48', '2014-11-03 01:30:48', 'For the kids, it''s obvious! What better way to follow up an amazing birthday party magic show than with their very own magical props?\r\n\r\nFor you, it''s a <strong>great bargain</strong>! Along with getting the items for less than their retail price, you''ll also be buying <span style="text-decoration: underline;">only the number of loot bags or wands needed on the day of the party!</span> That means you don''t have to worry about buying extras "just in case", and you don''t get stuck with leftovers if less children show up than expected.', 'What makes these magicians party bags and wands such a great deal?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'what-makes-these-magicians-party-bags-and-wands-such-a-great-deal', '', '', '2014-11-03 01:36:37', '2014-11-03 01:36:37', '', 0, 'http://localhost/magictoronto/?post_type=key-points&#038;p=189', 0, 'key-points', '', 0);
